Introduction

Lee Juchan is a South Korean trainee.

In September 2018, he was a contestant on KBS2's variety show Dancing High but was sadly eliminated.

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7 starting in October 2024.
